fields.description: a very good way to enlarge your bicep and make it strong

fields.name: Technogym Excite Run 700 Treadmill
fields.description: Technogym Excite Run Treadmills add a new level of style and sophistication to any fitness area or facility and offers a unique running experience that feels as natural as running outdoors.
fields.image: BH Fitness Pioneer R7 Treadmill (Touchscreen Console).jpg

fields.name: HIT FITNESS G6 Indoor Cycling Bike
fields.description: The G6 Indoor Cycle by Hit Fitness is a great value home grade exercise bike. The G6 is of very solid construction, and feels remarkably smooth and stable, with an excellent range of resistance. The Bike has a very sturdy and robust frame giving you a long-lasting product life and the ability to support users with a weight of up to 125kg (20st). The G6 can also track your workout and fitness journey via the display console which provides you real-time data on your time, calories burned and speed. For extra peace of mind this bike also comes with 1 year home warranty.

fields.name: Hit Fitness Air Runner Curved Treadmill
fields.description:
The Hit Fitness Air Runner Curved Treadmill redefines the manual treadmill, offering superior steel construction, dependable stability, and functionality in a streamlined, energy-efficient design. Air runners burn up to 30% more calories than motorized treadmills. It encourages a natural running feel and promotes more efficient running strides than regular treadmills.

Air treadmills are much easier on the environment than regular treadmills, as they run solely on your energy with zero electrical consumption. You’ll be playing your part for a better planet while improving your own health and fitness. With the Hit Fitness Air Runner, you will experience a complete running routine right from the comfort of your home. With a constant feeling like you’re running on air, you can rest assured your new running routine will rival any cardio routine.
fields.image: hit fitness air runner curved trademilll.jpg

fields.name: NordicTrack S10i Indoor Bike
fields.description: iFit Coach Ready is with iFit interactive technology, you can bike anywhere in the world. Choose from pre-mapped courses or create your own. Tapping into Google Maps, this NordicTrack indoor cycle is iFit Coach Ready and automatically simulates every hill and dip. Plus, you can track your progress automatically, compete with friends, and customise your workout to match your goals. iFit can be purchased on a yearly subscription for an additional cost.

fields.name: Olympic Competition Bumper Plate  20kg
fields.description: These HIT Fitness weight plates have been meticulously designed in order to accommodate competitive Olympic weightlifting standards as well as high quality and accurate training regimens. The main advantages that are associated with these plates include effective bounce reduction, thinner plate widths which allow more plates to be loaded on to a barbell, and their weight tolerance must be within +/- 1% of their assigned weight. Additionally, the attractive and bold features of these plates will enhance your gym's appearance and make lifters stand out on the platform.

fields.name: Precor TRM731 Treadmill
fields.description: The TRM731 is a line treadmill that combines essential reliability and ease-of-use with an intuitive console at a value just right for you. This treadmill is designed to optimize performance and maintenance while providing a comfortable and effective workout for your exercisers. The simple, clean design holds up under heavy commercial use, ensuring your investment will last into the future.

fields.name: Assault AirRunner
fields.description: The Assault AirRunner is a premier elite fitness running machine that packs an intense workout into a small package. The name says it all - it's like running on air, but with a powerful amount of punch.

fields.name: HIT FITNESS Destroyer Air Bike
fields.description: The Destroyer Dual-Action Air Bike is a stationary bike that offers an intense full-body workout with a twist. This exercise bike will help you strengthen your lower body and arms simultaneously while working up a huge sweat. This all-in-one cross trainer will push your strength and endurance to its limits, allowing you to sculpt your dream body as you please. This cross-trainer bike comes with a user-friendly LCD tracker that allows you to experience different workouts depending on your taste or mood. You can choose to track your time, distance, speed, heart rate, and various other modes, ensuring you’re always engaged with new challenges. The Air Bike is ergonomically designed with your comfort and safety in mind. Its adjustable seat and handlebars are carefully designed to prevent you from experiencing back stiffness, strains, and muscle aches. With the Dual-Action Destroyer Air Bike, you will experience a complete cardio routine right from the comfort of your home. With easy-to-follow assembly instructions, you can rest assured your new home routine will rival any gym workout.

fields.name: Sole Fitness LCR Recumbent Exercise Bike
fields.description:
The Sole Light Commercial recumbent cycle (LCR) is the perfect piece of exercise equipment for almost every need. Built to be durable using quality materials, the Sole LCR has set a new standard for indoor recumbent exercise cycles.

At Sole, designers have engineered a light commercial recumbent cycle that holds up under consistent use and provides support and comfort to all users. Stable and durable, the Sole LCR boasts 40 levels of resistance to challenge any user regardless of their fitness level. The supportive back and adjustable seat, stationary handlebars, and seat-mounted side handlebars with heart rate grips are perfect for the needs of multiple users. The LCR is ideal for use in light commercial settings or smaller spaces as it is compact and easy to set up.

The Sole LCR is an ideal workout for any workout level and a comfortable and versatile method toward achieving fitness. The LCR is equipped with Bluetooth technology allowing users to record workout feedback from their cycle to an Android or Apple smart device, and track fitness info on the free Sole Fitness App, or transfer it to compatible fitness apps. Sole Fitness App, or transfer it to other compatible fitness apps.

Sole’s LCR is the perfect recumbent bike for people looking to stay in shape without the risk of pain. The LCR is top rated because it provides incredible value and is the most functional recumbent bike on the market. Whether you run a physical therapy office or a simple fitness studio, this bike is the perfect addition

fields.name: Sole Fitness CC81 Cardio Climber
fields.description:
Sole Fitness CC81 Cardio Climber is a full-body vertical workout that targets all major muscle groups: Arms, ABS, shoulders, back, glutes, hips, and legs in a single fluid motion.
Combining elements of both elliptical and climber products, it is easier on the joints and very effective at toning the entire body. All in one effective workout!

fields.name: Versaclimber CL-108SM Sport Model
fields.description: The 108 SM has been refined and improved for a new generation of health & fitness enthusiasts. Like the interactive "smart" module w/voice feedback, sleek curves and a space efficient 3 point base. Every time you train on the SM you can choose to hear a clear voice feedback during your work out--its like having your personal trainer with you every step of the way. Its great for instruction, motivational training commands and overall VersaClimber training tips. Also choose a variety of virtual opponents to challenge or select famous towers, structures and mountains. The SM features the classic, calorie guzzling, versatile 1-20 inch step height combined with the 1-20 inch upper body arm movement. The SM offers a wider range of cardio & strength versatility. From its ability to apply long muscle toning leg strides to explosive sprint training movements, and every type of cardio training in between to meet your specific training requirements.

fields.name: Hit Fitness Aerobic Step
fields.description: The Hit Fitness Aerobic Step is a versatile piece of equipment the step is compact, light and easily portable. With 3 different height adjustments the step allows you to perform a wide variety of workouts. Suitable for aerobic stepping, leg balance exercises, plank and assisted plank, press-ups, sit-ups, plyometric training and much much more - the Hit Fitness Step is the perfect tool to get in shape.

fields.name: The Reebok Step
fields.description: Variety in training is key to progress and with the Reebok Aerobic Step, no two workouts are ever the same. This is the ideal platform for group classes to perform a large range of basic and more complex exercises from cardiovascular and plyometric training to lower body muscle toning; its versatility is ideal for mixing up any workout programme. Suitable for all abilities and fitness levels, the modern red and black Reebok Step can be combined with mat work exercises, or used with hand, wrist or ankle weights for an even higher calorie burn. Popular in gym class settings, the step is often incorporated into choreographed routines to upbeat music.

fields.name: Sole E25 Elliptical Cross Trainer
fields.description: The SOLE E25's fluid natural motion is ensured by a whisper-quiet drive system that functions in both forward and reverse motion. The E25 is engineered for an extremely smooth feel, even with increased resistance for when you want a more challenging workout. Oversized foot pedals situated at a 2 ° inward angle sustain your body's natural position and reduce the impact on the joints and muscles

fields.name: Endura-Fitness®-Infinity-X-Trainer-PRO
fields.description:
The robust Endura Fitness® Infinity X-Trainer PRO has everything you need for your most challenging training session yet. The trainer has a 20 inch stride length, 10.6 inch step-up height an 9.8 inch pedal spacing. This makes the Endura Fitness® Infinity X-Trainer PRO one of the most well-designed crosstrainers on the market when it comes to ergonomics.

The Infinity X-Trainer PRO is a high-end commercial product designed to go above and beyond the demands of a fully working health club or gym. Due to the robust construction, this crosstrainer can support a maximum user weight of 182KG. Powered by an electromagnetic braking system and a brushless hybrid generator, the Infinity X-Trainer PRO delivers 30 challenging resistance levels. This machine has a 15.6″ Android Touchscreen display with WiFi, MP3 and TV connectivity, this will keep your clients entertained while training and have them coming back for more

fields.name: Sole Fitness E35 Cross Trainer
fields.description:
The E35 is engineered for an extremely smooth feel, even with increased resistance for when you want a more challenging workout. Fluid natural motion is ensured by four wheels gliding along dual rails and functions in both forward and reverse.
Warranty: Home Use, up to 2hrs use per day in a suitable home environment.
Multi-grip position handlebars enable users to find the most comfortable and ergonomic positions to grasp the handles, while oversized foot pedals situated at a 2° inward angle, and 3-position articulating foot beds sustain your body's natural position and reduce impact on joints and muscles. The E35’s power incline feature offers additional resistance and variable positions, allowing you to individually target major lower body muscle groups while the articulating handles provide upper body exercise for a total body workout

fields.name: BH Fitness I.Cross 3000 Hiit Elliptical Cross Trainer
fields.description:
The i.Cross 3000 HIIT Elliptical Cross Trainer is the answer for those who want to lose weight or build muscle by doing HIIT (high-intensity interval training), as well as standard cardio sessions.
This trainer has a fan to keep you cool while training from regular to very high intensity while will in no time give you the results that you require along with a regular eating plan. The most important step that you take after training is your next meal to yield the results.

fields.name: Hit Fitness Olympic Competition Bumper Plate  5kg
fields.description:
The York 135KG Olympic Weight Set is a perfect choice for any home gym. This complete Olympic set uses the new York G2 Steel Olympic Plates which feature an innovative interlocking design, as well as easy to grab handles and edges that make the plate much easier to pickup.
York have been manufacturing bars for 80+ years and this is perfect for Olympic bench press, shoulder press, deadlifts, lunges and overhead presses. Solid steel, finished in an attractive chromed finish this bar will be the pride of your home gym.

fields.name: Endura Fitness Infinity Olympic Rubber Grip Plates
fields.description:
The Endura Fitness infinity Olympic rubber grip weight plates are an excellent choice of weight plate for standard lifting, where you don’t aim to drop the weights. They have a solid cast metal core and are coated with a high quality smooth, yet very thick and durable rubber. This helps to ensure that the metal core is protected and helps to protect floors and other weight plates from impacts. The tri-grip design places three cut-outs around the plate for easy carrying. Whilst the plate lugs help to reduce the chance of finger trapping and they lock together to stop plates from rotating against each other.
Available in the following weight plates 1.25 kg, 2.5 kg, 5kg, 10kg, 15kg, 20kg and 25kg. These weight plates are perfect for powerlifting and general weight training. So stack up your bar today with Endura Fitness and start making those gains.

fields.name: Hit Fitness Kettlebell with Chrome Handle | 28kg
fields.description:
HIT Fitness kettlebells are considered to be the best kettlebells in the fitness industry when it comes to constantly providing superior performance, durability, longevity, comfort, and secure grip.
All our HIT Fitness kettlebells come with a smooth, imperfection free surface finish which reduces any friction between the athlete and the kettlebell. This makes performing kettlebell exercises more comfortable and fluid. HIT Fitness kettlebells are designed with athletes in mind. The polished chrome handles have been manufactured to provide optimal grip to athletes whilst also complementing the HIT Fitness kettlebell colours and design. Our HIT Fitness kettlebells with the chrome handle finish are available in weight increments between 4 - 28kg.

fields.name: Hit Fitness Steel Competition Kettlebell  32kg
fields.description: HIT FITNESS competition kettlebells are made from steel with a large unpainted handle attached to the top of the ball. Kettlebells can be used to perform many types of exercises. Ballistic style training, which combines cardiovascular training, strength training and flexibility training, primarily utilise kettlebells for a variety of exercises. HIT FITNESS competition kettlebells meet international competitive standards of kettlebell lifting and come in one size for all weights.

fields.name: Hit Fitness Steel Competition Kettlebell  8kg
fields.description: HIT FITNESS competition kettlebells are made from steel with a large unpainted handle attached to the top of the ball. Kettlebells can be used to perform many types of exercises. Ballistic style training, which combines cardiovascular training, strength training and flexibility training, primarily utilise kettlebells for a variety of exercises. HIT FITNESS competition kettlebells meet international competitive standards of kettlebell lifting and come in one size for all weights

fields.name: Hit Fitness Adjustable Dumbbells  25kg Pair
fields.description: The Adjustable Dumbbells by Hit Fitness are essentially 10 dumbbells of varying weights merged into one. Simply just hold the button and twist the dial to select your desired weight. These dumbbells are a must for those of you who want a selection of dumbbells but lack the necessary storage space and more importantly, time

fields.name: Hit Fitness Adjustable Dumbbells  40kg Pair
fields.description: The Adjustable Dumbbell by HIT FITNESS is essentially 12 dumbbells of varying weights merged into one. Simply just hold the button and twist the dial to select your desired weight. These dumbbells are a must for those of you who want a selection of dumbbells but lack the necessary storage space and more importantly, time.

fields.name: Hit Fitness Rubber Studio Dumbbell | 1kg
fields.description: HIT Fitness has created a line of beautifully crafted studio dumbbells that are aimed at improving the functionality of exercise classes. HIT Fitness studio dumbbells have been engineered and designed with studio classes and high-intensity interval training workouts in mind.

fields.name: Jordan Ignite V2 Urethane Dumbbells 17.5kg-25kg
fields.description: Great-value rubber dumbbells featuring our classic design, this versatile dumbbell suits commercial, boutique gyms as well as home users.

fields.name: HIT FITNESS Spring Collars 50mm | Pair
fields.description: These 2" stainless steel spring collars are an essential accompaniment to our bumper plates and barbells for any Olympic lifting or strength and conditioning program. They slide onto barbells easily allowing for fast transition between plate changes. They are secure and will keep plates firmly in place during lifts.

fields.name: HIT FITNESS Hex Bar 1.6m
fields.description: High grade electroplated hex bar suitable for performing deadlifts. An alternative to the traditional barbell, the hex bar offers additional lumbar support to other barbells, allowing users to lift heavier weight more comfortably. The bar is suitable for use on its own or with plates.

fields.name: Hit Fitness Battle Ropes
fields.description:
Hit Fitness Battle Ropes help build both stamina and strength simultaneously and was voted the best cardio workout by Men's Health Magazine. You can use this exercise as a main workout or for a finisher to top off your workout. Also called slam ropes, these ropes combine high-intensity work with strength and help you work multiple muscle groups at once.
These ropes are made of highly durable material to withstand the punishment of your workouts.

fields.name: Hit Fitness Battle Rope | 15m X 40mm
fields.description: The HIT FITNESS multi-functional new design battle rope can be used for a large variety of strength and conditioning training purposes. Battle ropes are brilliant for high intensity upper and lower body conditioning and cardiovascular exercise routines.

fields.name: Tunturi Strength Bag
fields.description: Increase your strength, stability and stamina. Four sturdy handles and is suitable for different strength exercises. Solid fitness bag with different handles for training your arms, legs, shoulders and back. Durable material: can be used both indoor and outdoor. Combination of a kettlebell, medicine ball and weight bar. Weight is easy to adjust by removing sandbags 56 cm long

fields.name: Sand bag weights
fields.description: Sandbag weights are also known as powerbags, and they are an excellent piece of fitness equipment. No matter if you’re working out at the gym or outside, these durable, heavy duty sandbags have been designed for high intensity workouts. We have power bag style sandbag weights that have multiple handles, allowing them to be used for a wide variety of exercises. They can be carried and lifted, you can squat them, drag them, pass them, there’s so many training options. You can build strength, muscle and power from anywhere. Our power bags start at 5 KG and go up to 25 KG making them ideal for anyone from beginners all the way to highly conditioned athletes. Sandbag weights are perfect for core strength and abdominal conditioning. These durable sandbags are suitable for a wide range of compound exercises, strength training and full body workouts. Transform your workout today
